iv><div>3. Homeless 17 Year Old Living Under Bridge Who Surrendered 4 Month Old Puppy So It Would Be Taken Care Of Reunited With Dog - "He left Jada there with a bag of dog food."  This broke me. He's homeless, doesn't even have a tent anymore, and he still has dog food. But good news, he has a place to stay now with his dog</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0eCNGaI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>"This conservative pushback is actually generating a lot of interest in books that might not be something the average student is being exposed to otherwise,"</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/I2yfJ2I.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>5. Wildflower believed to be extinct for 40 years spotted in Ecuador - Gasteranthus extinctus was found by biologists in the foothills of the Andes mountains and in remnant patches of forest in the Centinela region of Ecuador, almost 40 years after its last sighting.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Iy4vZFj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>6. Wildlife Sanctuaries Welcome Lions, Tigers Rescued From Circuses - Four Bengal tigers and four lions have been rescued, after much of their lives were spent in circuses and tight living quarters, as part of two rescue operations. They will now live in wildlife sanctuaries in South Africa.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JCXBLRL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>7. 'Historic': global climate plans can now keep heating below 2C, study shows - For the first time the world is in a position to limit global heating to under 2C, according to the first in-depth analysis of the net zero pledges made by nations at the UN Cop26 climate summit in December.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Gnk2FQy.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>That's it for this week :) Until next week, you can find the sources and read my previous posts on my blog here https://feelgoodnews.substack.com/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xmakHQD</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[FeelGoodNews]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Mom’s bout to drop bombs</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/LEkyh42</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qotDAUz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>@TaRhondaThomas on Twitter</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/LEkyh42</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Holykin1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I AGREE WITH THESE GUYS, THEIR SUPPORTERS ARE ALL SNOWFLAKES</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/XYQEzgh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sWq7wwQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Link to tweet:

